{"title":"Android_End","uid":"c6514010f10f74959b0358300a9b00fc","slug":"Android-End","date":"2024-05-01T05:33:39.000Z","updated":"2024-11-15T12:54:20.593Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android-End.json","keywords":null,"cover":"cover/cover3.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"课程串讲\"><a href=\"#课程串讲\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"课程串讲\"></a>课程串讲</h1><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501134625908.png\" alt=\"image-20240501134625908\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"课程目标\"><a href=\"#课程目标\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"课程目标\"></a>课程目标</h2><ul>\n<li>掌握Android平台进行移动应用程序的设计、开发、测试、调试、发布等流程</li>\n<li>掌握企业工作重点实践内容、学习工作中实践问题详解、学习性能优化、掌握高阶工程师开发必备的技能</li>\n<li>学习源码知识，掌握通过源码解决问题的能力</li>\n<li>完成实践课程，完成由理论到实践的转变</li>\n<li>完成一个上线App所有基础知识、进阶知识</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"一、Activity-Fragment\"><a href=\"#一、Activity-Fragment\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、Activity+Fragment\"></a>一、Activity+Fragment</h2><h3 id=\"Activity生命周期方法\"><a href=\"#Activity生命周期方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Activity生命周期方法\"></a>Activity生命周期方法</h3><p><a href=\"https://developer.android.google.cn/guide/components/activities/activity-lifecycle?hl=zh-cn\">https://developer.android.google.cn/guide/components/activities/activity-lifecycle?hl=zh-cn</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501135148046.png\" alt=\"image-20240501135148046\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501135655423.png\" alt=\"image-20240501135655423\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"任务栈介绍\"><a href=\"#任务栈介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"任务栈介绍\"></a>任务栈介绍</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501135721695.png\" alt=\"image-20240501135721695\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"启动模式介绍\"><a href=\"#启动模式介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启动模式介绍\"></a>启动模式介绍</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501135815019.png\" alt=\"image-20240501135815019\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Intent\"><a href=\"#Intent\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Intent\"></a>Intent</h3><p>通过直接设置组件名称调起组件调起指定Activity。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501140006337.png\" alt=\"image-20240501140006337\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Fragment的诞生\"><a href=\"#Fragment的诞生\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Fragment的诞生\"></a>Fragment的诞生</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501140141771.png\" alt=\"image-20240501140141771\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Fragment与Activity的关系\"><a href=\"#Fragment与Activity的关系\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Fragment与Activity的关系\"></a>Fragment与Activity的关系</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501140249558.png\" alt=\"image-20240501140249558\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"创建Fragment\"><a href=\"#创建Fragment\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建Fragment\"></a>创建Fragment</h2><p>在res&#x2F;layout文件夹下，创建example_fragment.xml布局文件</p>\n<p>创建ExampleFragment，继承Fragment类，并向基本构造函数提供Fragment的布局资源</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501140314268.png\" alt=\"image-20240501140314268\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"动态添加Fragment\"><a href=\"#动态添加Fragment\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"动态添加Fragment\"></a>动态添加Fragment</h3><p>在代码中创建和管理，在运行时动态添加、替换和移除，独立于布局文件不需要在XML布局文件中通过android:name属性声明具体的Fragment类</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501140338793.png\" alt=\"image-20240501140338793\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Fragment与Activity通信\"><a href=\"#Fragment与Activity通信\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Fragment与Activity通信\"></a>Fragment与Activity通信</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501140454617.png\" alt=\"image-20240501140454617\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Fragment间通信\"><a href=\"#Fragment间通信\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Fragment间通信\"></a>Fragment间通信</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501140526475.png\" alt=\"image-20240501140526475\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"二、基础UI\"><a href=\"#二、基础UI\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、基础UI\"></a>二、基础UI</h2><h3 id=\"TextView介绍\"><a href=\"#TextView介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"TextView介绍\"></a>TextView介绍</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501143346020.png\" alt=\"image-20240501143346020\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Button介绍\"><a href=\"#Button介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Button介绍\"></a>Button介绍</h3><p>Button：在UI上生成一个按钮，可供用户单击，当用户单击按钮时，触发一个onclick事件Button是TextView的子类，所以TextView上很多属性也可以应用到Button上！实际开发中对于Button的使用，主要对按钮的几个状态做相应的操作，比如：按钮按下的时候用一种样式，松开又一种样式，或者按钮不可用的时候一种样式等等。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501143452124.png\" alt=\"image-20240501143452124\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"EditText\"><a href=\"#EditText\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"EditText\"></a>EditText</h3><p>EditText：车输入框，是用户和Android应用进行数据传递的通道，通过它，我们可以获取到用户输入的数据。EditText是一个输入框，在开发中也是经常使用到的一个控件，常用于需要获取用户输入的场景，例如：登录注册功能、搜索功能、反馈功能等。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501143558716.png\" alt=\"image-20240501143558716\"></p>\n<p>EditText输入限制获取末尾输入，若不是数字，贝则删除末尾字符，重新设置光标。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501143653642.png\" alt=\"image-20240501143653642\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"EditText输入限制\"><a href=\"#EditText输入限制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"EditText输入限制\"></a>EditText输入限制</h4><p>drawable_button_enable.xml</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501143841470.png\" alt=\"image-20240501143841470\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"EditText光标移动和选择\"><a href=\"#EditText光标移动和选择\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"EditText光标移动和选择\"></a>EditText光标移动和选择</h4><p>setSelection()方法</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>setSelection(intindex)把光标移动到指定位置</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>setSelection(int start, int stop)选择范围</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501144008358.png\" alt=\"image-20240501144008358\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"ImageView介绍\"><a href=\"#ImageView介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ImageView介绍\"></a>ImageView介绍</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501144111852.png\" alt=\"image-20240501144111852\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501144231582.png\" alt=\"image-20240501144231582\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"RecyclerView实现列表\"><a href=\"#RecyclerView实现列表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"RecyclerView实现列表\"></a>RecyclerView实现列表</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501144953062.png\" alt=\"image-20240501144953062\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"RecyclerView实现列表-1\"><a href=\"#RecyclerView实现列表-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"RecyclerView实现列表\"></a>RecyclerView实现列表</h4><h3 id=\"屏幕适配方案介绍\"><a href=\"#屏幕适配方案介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"屏幕适配方案介绍\"></a>屏幕适配方案介绍</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501145132994.png\" alt=\"image-20240501145132994\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501145243786.png\" alt=\"image-20240501145243786\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501151745786.png\" alt=\"image-20240501151745786\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"三、基础布局\"><a href=\"#三、基础布局\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、基础布局\"></a>三、基础布局</h2><h2 id=\"四、组件库的使用\"><a href=\"#四、组件库的使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、组件库的使用\"></a>四、组件库的使用</h2><h3 id=\"组件库-依赖方式\"><a href=\"#组件库-依赖方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件库-依赖方式\"></a>组件库-依赖方式</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501150356818.png\" alt=\"image-20240501150356818\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501150655354.png\" alt=\"image-20240501150655354\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"组件库-瀑布流\"><a href=\"#组件库-瀑布流\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件库-瀑布流\"></a>组件库-瀑布流</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501151343895.png\" alt=\"image-20240501151343895\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501151414580.png\" alt=\"image-20240501151414580\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501151430160.png\" alt=\"image-20240501151430160\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"组件库-适配器组件\"><a href=\"#组件库-适配器组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件库-适配器组件\"></a>组件库-适配器组件</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501151520048.png\" alt=\"image-20240501151520048\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501151546669.png\" alt=\"image-20240501151546669\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"组件库-下拉刷新\"><a href=\"#组件库-下拉刷新\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件库-下拉刷新\"></a>组件库-下拉刷新</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501151645147.png\" alt=\"image-20240501151645147\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"组件库-上拉加载\"><a href=\"#组件库-上拉加载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件库-上拉加载\"></a>组件库-上拉加载</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501151703471.png\" alt=\"image-20240501151703471\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"五、http请求、数据解析和权限\"><a href=\"#五、http请求、数据解析和权限\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、http请求、数据解析和权限\"></a>五、http请求、数据解析和权限</h2><h3 id=\"权限类型\"><a href=\"#权限类型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"权限类型\"></a>权限类型</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501153344628.png\" alt=\"image-20240501153344628\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501153357857.png\" alt=\"image-20240501153357857\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501153543615.png\" alt=\"image-20240501153543615\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"okhttp\"><a href=\"#okhttp\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"okhttp\"></a>okhttp</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501153620630.png\" alt=\"image-20240501153620630\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Get请求\"><a href=\"#Get请求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get请求\"></a>Get请求</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501153756342.png\" alt=\"image-20240501153756342\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"OkHttp使用\"><a href=\"#OkHttp使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"OkHttp使用\"></a>OkHttp使用</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501153846715.png\" alt=\"image-20240501153846715\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501153949935.png\" alt=\"image-20240501153949935\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Post请求\"><a href=\"#Post请求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Post请求\"></a>Post请求</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501154048922.png\" alt=\"image-20240501154048922\"></p>\n<p>使用OkHttp进行Post请求，同时RequestBody使用json提交数据</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501154123083.png\" alt=\"image-20240501154123083\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"GSON\"><a href=\"#GSON\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"GSON\"></a>GSON</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501154232957.png\" alt=\"image-20240501154232957\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Handler\"><a href=\"#Handler\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Handler\"></a>Handler</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501154333673.png\" alt=\"image-20240501154333673\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"六、性能优化\"><a href=\"#六、性能优化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"六、性能优化\"></a>六、性能优化</h2><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sjwusj/imgbed@main/img/android/image-20240501154422434.png\" alt=\"image-20240501154422434\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"ViewsStub按需加载\"><a href=\"#ViewsStub按需加载\" class=